articles.author: Jamie Barton
articles.title: Caitlin Clark gets triple-double, flagrant foul for shoving Angel Reese in season-opening win - CNN
articles.description: Caitlin Clark had an eventful season opener on Saturday, claiming the third triple-double of her WNBA career and receiving a flagrant foul for a shove on long-time rival Angel Reese, as the Indiana Fever routed the Chicago Sky 93-58.
